Description:Blue Elemental Blast destroy mode — P2 casts BEB on P1's Mons's Goblin Raiders (a genuinely RED creature); it is destroyed and moves to its owner's graveyard. A basic Mountain is colorless (CR 105.2a: a land type does not grant color), so BEB's "destroy target red permanent" may NOT target a Mountain — the legal target must actually be red.

